productReviews.reviewText: one of my hobbies is antique-shopping. and when i'm antique-shopping this works great.
My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 yard and weights 19 pound!!!
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
